Class LoadObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.server.commonClasses.helperClasses.LoadObject

  • public class LoadObject
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Cory on 3/19/17. This class represents the format of the request data for the /load API endpoint. It includes arrays of the 3 main data types for our Family Map database.
